mmary\r\n\r\n  This PR introduces a new workflow for releasing KSC (Klever Smart Contract meta tool) binaries to cloud storage and includes important dependency updates to address security vulnerabilities.\r\n\r\n  ## Changes\r\n\r\n  ### \ud83d\ude80 New Features\r\n  - **KSC Cloud Release Workflow** (`release-ksc-cloud.yml`):\r\n    - Manual trigger workflow for building and uploading KSC binaries to Google Cloud Storage\r\n    - Multi-platform support: Linux (x86_64), macOS (ARM64 & x86_64), and Windows (x86_64)\r\n    - Binary renamed from `sc-meta` to `ksc` for clearer branding\r\n    - Optimized for GitHub's pre-installed Rust toolchain\r\n\r\n  - **Proxy Comparison Workflow** (`proxy-compare.yml`):\r\n    - Automated workflow to compare newly generated proxy files with existing ones\r\n    - Helps maintain consistency in proxy generation\r\n\r\n  ### \ud83d\udd27 Improvements\r\n  - **Release Workflow Enhancement**:\r\n    - Removed manual dispatch inputs from main release workflow for cleaner automation\r\n    - Improved tag validation and error messaging\r\n\r\n  - **Template Generation**:\r\n    - Enhanced proxy module renaming logic to handle both `proxy_name` and `name_proxy` patterns\r\n    - Fixed issues with lib.rs file renaming in templates\r\n\r\n  - **WebAssembly Build System Enhancement**: \r\n    - Added support for Rust 1.85's new `wasm32v1-none` target\r\n    - Implemented automatic target detection based on Rust version\r\n    - Enhanced wasm tools installation with better target handling\r\n    - Improved contract variant builder for dynamic target selection\r\n  \r\n  ### \ud83d\udd12 Security Updates\r\n  - Updated `zip` crate from 2.1 to 4.0.0 (addresses security vulnerability)\r\n  - Updated `ed25519-dalek` to 2.1.0 with API compatibility fixes\r\n  - Updated `indicatif` to 0.17.0\r\n\r\n  ### \ud83c\udfaf Other Changes\r\n  - Renamed CI workflow files for better clarity\r\n  - Fixed missing output value in koperator setup action\r\n  - Updated various proxy files to latest generated versions\r\n\r\n  ## Testing\r\n  - All existing tests pass\r\n  - Template generation tests verified with crypto-zombies example\r\n  - Dependency updates tested with cargo check/build\r\n\r\n  ## Breaking Changes\r\n  None - all changes are backward compatible", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/issues/8/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/issues/8/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/issues/7", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/issues/7/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/issues/7/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/issues/7/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/pull/7", "id": 2986469669, "node_id": "PR_kwDOLjSxr86SJJoH", "number": 7, "title": "Fix: split rustup update and target add commands in workflow", "user": {"login": "fbsobreira", "id": 8503176, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjg1MDMxNzY=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8503176?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/fbsobreira", "html_url": "https://github.com/fbsobreira", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fbsobreira/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fbsobreira/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fbsobreira/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fbsobreira/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/fbsobreira/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "http