ed_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 0, "created_at": "2025-04-07T15:01:57Z", "updated_at": "2025-04-09T23:05:08Z", "closed_at": "2025-04-09T23:05:08Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "type": null, "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/pulls/5", "html_url": "https://github.com/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/pull/5", "diff_url": "https://github.com/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/pull/5.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/pull/5.patch", "merged_at": "2025-04-09T23:05:08Z"}, "body": "## \ud83d\udce6 Release v0.44.0\r\n\r\nThis PR merges `release/44.0` into `master`, finalizing the v0.44.0 SDK release. The release includes major features, compatibility upgrades, improved benchmarks, and several internal refactors across contracts.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### \u2728 Key Features & Improvements\r\n\r\n#### \ud83e\udde9 New Capabilities\r\n- **Contract deletion** support and example (`KLC-1444`)\r\n- **Upgrade from source** using new semantic syntax (`KLC-1434`)\r\n- **Hooks Improvements** improved KDA token hook logic ([`KLC-1122`], [`KLC-939`]) and new hooks for `CallValues`\r\n- **Support for `has_role_transfer`** in `RolesInfo` struct\r\n- **Add `upgrade()` method** for stateful contract versioning\r\n\r\n#### \ud83e\uddea Benchmark & Test Suite Enhancements\r\n- New proxy layers (e.g. `LinkedListRepeatProxy`, `AdderProxy`)\r\n- Reworked test scenarios using new JSON interface style\r\n- Added `mb_builder_benchmark()` for ManagedBuffer stress tests\r\n\r\n#### \ud83d\udd01 Internal Refactors & Cleanup\r\n- Unified `klever_sc::imports!()` via `use` for consistency\r\n- Removed outdated wasm adapter comments and features\r\n- Cleaned redundant imports and streamlined `panic_handler` usage\r\n\r\n#### \ud83d\udd04 Compatibility & Version Updates\r\n- SDK updates from MultiversX **0.43.4 \u2192 0.50.4**\r\n- Updated dependencies: `syn`, `proc-macro2`, `base64`, `sha2`, `itertools`, etc.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### \ud83e\uddec Modules & Contracts Touched\r\n\r\n- `adder`, `linked-list-repeat`, `set-repeat`, `queue-repeat`, `map-repeat`, `vec-repeat`\r\n- `bonding-curve-contract`, `send-tx-repeat`, `str-repeat`, `check-pause`\r\n- Test suites refactored across all example and benchmark contracts\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### \ud83d\udee0 Internal Changes\r\n\r\n- \u2705 Converted macro-style imports to idiomatic `use` syntax\r\n- \u2705 Introduced proxy contracts with auto-generated `.rs` bindings\r\n- \u2705 Better path resolution for WASM adapter\r\n- \u2705 Upgraded scenario tests to the new modular testing framework\r\n- \u2705 CI Improvements\r\n- \u2705 Linting fixes\r\n", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/issues/5/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/issues/5/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/issues/4", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/issues/4/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/issues/4/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/issues/4/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/klever-io/klever-vm-sdk-rs/pull/4", "id": 2957292872, "node_id": "PR_kwDOLjSxr86QnmWm", "number": 4, "title": "[KLC-1438] Replace klever.finance with klever.org", "user": {"login": "nickgs1337", "id": 16809614, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE2ODA5NjE0", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.